.TH wrp_satmask 1 "February 2026" "arma-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
wrp_satmask \- generate an RGB surface-mask GeoTIFF from WRP data
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wrp_satmask
.RI [ flags ]
.I input.wrp output.tif
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wrp_satmask
renders per-cell dominant material categories into an RGB GeoTIFF and writes materials metadata JSON.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B
--pretty
Pretty-print materials JSON.
.TP
.BI "-offset-x " n
X coordinate offset (default 200000).
.TP
.BI "-offset-z " n
Z coordinate offset (default 0).
.TP
.BI "-materials " path
Output path for
.BR materials.json .
.TP
.BR -h , " --help"
Show help.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wrp_heightmap (1)
